<br>
1) Do we wish to use it?<br>
2) If so, do we want it separated into categories?<br>
- Money (and what would the money be used for?)<br>
- Tradeskill Items<br>
- Spells and Research<br>
- Armor<br>
- Misc<br>
3) I have an open character slot and am willing to create a druid for the purpose of actually holding the items.  It is possible that one character may run out of room.  Are you willing to use a character slot for this purpose? <p><a href="//home.attbi.com/~geist22/lanadena2.jpg"><center>
<img src="//home.attbi.com/~geist22/lanadena2.jpg" border="0">
</a> 

</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/btheclanmaclear.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=jeffryn>Jeffryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kin</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#330000>(2/8/02 1:40:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1391.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Guild Vaults</span><hr size=1> I believe I have two slots open, plus Tabong, brother of Yaibong (9th Mage I never play anymore,) if extra space is needed.<br>
<br>
...but I kinda feel that anybody holding items should have at least Thane (or Officer) status. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/btheclanmaclear.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ravnanger>Ravnanger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble</span><br>  Posts: 209<br> <font color=#330000>(2/8/02 4:34:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1391.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Guild Vaults</span><hr size=1> AS the realm turns.... we need a banker anyway. This would help organize it and since we already use GuildMagic for the roster........<br>
<br>
I can free up a slot also since I don't play my alts much anymore. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Scratches his head trying to think which one is his least favorite.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
