<img src="//home.attbi.com/~geist22/ravnanger.jpg"
border="0">
</a</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ulanadena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanadena</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Chief of Norrath</span><br>  Posts: 1006<br> <font color=#330000>(2/11/02 1:38:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1391.topic&index=10>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Guild Vaults</span><hr size=1> Each person would be responsible for working out the details with the other.  Another clan member could be used for the transfer if necessary.  (For example, you gave me SoW potions for Timo and I gave you the money.  When I saw Timo the next night, I gave him the SoW potions he had purchased.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=1391.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=1391.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1391.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=1391.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><b